-- Arkema CEO Wants to Keep Company Independent, Investir Reports
-- B y   M a r i e   M a w a d
-- 2012-07-07T08:12:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-07/arkema-ceo-wants-to-keep-company-independent-investir-reports.html
Arkema SA (AKE)  will seek to stay
independent and focus on its own growth strategy, Chief
Executive Officer Thierry Le Henaff told  Investir .  Le Henaff declined to comment on reports of takeover
approaches that caused the stock of the French maker of
specialty chemicals and additives to jump yesterday, according
to the weekly.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marie Mawad in Paris at 
